hwVoCallHistoryMaxLen.name: hwVoCallHistoryMaxLen
hwVoCallHistoryMaxLen.description: The maximum number of entries that the hwVoCallHistoryGenericTable, hwVoCallHistoryVoIPTable and hwVoCallHistoryPSTNTable may contain. The value 0 means that any history entry will not be saved. if these table are full, the oldest history entry will be deleted and the new one will be added.
